In a message dated 2/10/03 5:16:18 PM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "Alpha TRion?????"said Hydras with anger "so do you are an AUTOBOT?"
> 
Jumping to conclusions, wasn't he? she thought to herself. 

A dry soft laugh, "Hardly. As I said, I am a Decepticon." Narrowing her 
optics slightly, keeping them upon him. "If my information about you was 
correct, then that Megatron & Galvatron side of you would know who I am."

"Alpha Trion must have reactivated me for some reason. I was in a stasis lock 
on Cybertron in the Decepticon Crypt. Restored & reformated into this," 
moving her forearms & glancing at her form, "pathetic trans-organic form. 
Alpha Trion refused to give me back my form. When I was in search of 
materials to rebuild my own form the hard way, I was discovered by those who 
call themselves Tripredicus. Hardly worthy transformers. From there, I 
escaped in a shuttle." she held back the fact that there were materials in 
the shuttle, which Wheeljack was using to rebuild her form. 

--part1_39.33bbfd93.2b79f61a_boundary
